version_description:
The first update to Woodoku is here! We have improved the game’s sound effects and fixed a handful of bugs.

If you have any issues, please let us know at woodoku-support@tripledotstudios.com

We’ve fixed a few small bugs that were affecting players.

If you have any issues, please let us know at woodoku-support@tripledotstudios.com!

Thank you to all our wonderful fans for supporting our game! We’re always working to make Woodoku more beautiful and more fun.

Let us know what you think at woodoku-support@tripledotstudios.com!
